        Worst Quality: </br> <input type="text" name="worst" value="<%=ex.worst%>"> </br></br>
        Attractiveness Scale 1-10: <input type="range" min="1" max="10" name="attractiveness" value="<%=ex.attractiveness%>"></br></br>
        Do they have a sense of humor?</br><input type="radio" name="humor" value="yes"> So funny</br>
                                           <input type="radio" name="humor" value="kinda"> Kinda</br>
                                           <input type="radio" name="humor" value="no"> No sense of humor</br></br>
        Are they Cheap? <input type="radio" name="cheap" value="yes">yes
                        <input type="radio" name="cheap" value="no"> no </br></br>

        Good Attitude? <input type="radio" name="attitude" value="yes"> yes
                       <input type="radio" name="attitude" value="no"> no </br></br>
        Anything else you would like to add </br> <input type="text" name="description" value="<%=ex.description%>"></br>
        </br><input type="submit" value="Submit">
      </form>
    </br></br>
